                            We will reimburse You no later than 14 days from the day on which We receive the returned Goods. We will use the same means of payment as You used for the Order, and You will not incur any fees for such reimbursement.
                        </p>
                        <br>

                        <p
                            class="mb-5 primary-color-blackish-blue text-xl 2xl:text-4xl font-semibold px-4 lg:px-0 -mt-2 lg:-mt-0">
                            Conditions for Returns
                        </p>
                        <p
                            class="mb-5 primary-color-blackish-blue-opacity font-medium md:text-sm 2xl:text-3xl px-4 lg:px-0 2xl:px-4 lg:pr-3 mt-2 lg:-mt-1 2xl:mt-2 2xl:pb-64">
                            In order for the Goods to be eligible for a return, please make sure that:</p>
                        <p
                            class="mb-5 primary-color-blackish-blue-opacity font-medium md:text-sm 2xl:text-3xl px-4 lg:px-0 2xl:px-4 lg:pr-3 mt-2 lg:-mt-1 2xl:mt-2 2xl:pb-64">
                            1. The Goods were purchased in the last 7 days
                        </p>
                        <p
                            class="mb-5 primary-color-blackish-blue-opacity font-medium md:text-sm 2xl:text-3xl px-4 lg:px-0 2xl:px-4 lg:pr-3 mt-2 lg:-mt-1 2xl:mt-2 2xl:pb-64">
                            The following Goods cannot be returned:
                        </p>
                        <p
                            class="mb-5 primary-color-blackish-blue-opacity font-medium md:text-sm 2xl:text-3xl px-4 lg:px-0 2xl:px-4 lg:pr-3 mt-2 lg:-mt-1 2xl:mt-2 2xl:pb-64">
                            1. The supply of Goods made to Your specifications or clearly personalized.</p>
                        <p
                            class="mb-5 primary-color-blackish-blue-opacity font-medium md:text-sm 2xl:text-3xl px-4 lg:px-0 2xl:px-4 lg:pr-3 mt-2 lg:-mt-1 2xl:mt-2 2xl:pb-64">
                            2. The supply of Goods which according to their nature are not suitable to be returned, deteriorate rapidly or where the date of expiry is over.
                        </p>
                        <p
                            class="mb-5 primary-color-blackish-blue-opacity font-medium md:text-sm 2xl:text-3xl px-4 lg:px-0 2xl:px-4 lg:pr-3 mt-2 lg:-mt-1 2xl:mt-2 2xl:pb-64">
                            3. The supply of Goods which are not suitable for return due to health protection or hygiene reasons and were unsealed after delivery.
                        </p>
                        <p
                            class="mb-5 primary-color-blackish-blue-opacity font-medium md:text-sm 2xl:text-3xl px-4 lg:px-0 2xl:px-4 lg:pr-3 mt-2 lg:-mt-1 2xl:mt-2 2xl:pb-64">
                            4. The supply of Goods which are, after delivery, according to their nature, inseparably mixed with other items.
                        </p>
                        <p
                            class="mb-5 primary-color-blackish-blue-opacity font-medium md:text-sm 2xl:text-3xl px-4 lg:px-0 2xl:px-4 lg:pr-3 mt-2 lg:-mt-1 2xl:mt-2 2xl:pb-64">
                            We reserve the right to refuse returns of any merchandise that does not meet the above return conditions in our sole discretion.
